    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J18">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Gentian weaves her fringes --</l>
                    <l>The Maple's loom is red --</l>
                    <l>My departing blossoms</l>
                    <l>Obviate parade.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A brief, but patient illness --</l>
                    <l>An hour to prepare,</l>
                    <l>And one below, this morning</l>
                    <l>Is where the angels are --</l>
                    <l>It was a short procession,</l>
                    <l>The Bobolink was there --</l>
                    <l>An aged Bee addressed us --</l>
                    <l>And then we knelt in prayer --</l>
                    <l>We trust that she was willing --</l>
                    <l>We ask that we may be.</l>
                    <l>Summer -- Sister -- Seraph!</l>
                    <l>Let us go with thee!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>In the name of the Bee --</l>
                    <l>And of the Butterfly</l>
                    <l>And of the Breeze -- Amen!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
